data.description: Charming two-story home with a timeless white stucco facade and a distinctive tile roof. Nestled on a spacious lot, this property boasts a picturesque landscape adorned with several majestic palm trees. The well-maintained interior features four spacious rooms, loft, refrigerated a/c and much more. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and style in this inviting residence. Explore the beauty of indoor-outdoor living with a generously sized backyard, ideal for gatherings, cookouts,  etc. Step onto your expansive outdoor balcony, a serene retreat perched above your neighborhood. This spacious outdoor balcony is not just an extension of your living space; it's a sanctuary where you can escape the hustle and bustle, a canvas for creating memories. The home has some ADA modifications to accommodate a wheel chair. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your dream home. This listing is submitted subject to errors, omissions or changes without notice.
